    "title": "Urgent Opening Hotel Manager at Goa Tourism Holdings Services",
    "description": "Grow your career with Goa Tourism Holdings Services! We are hiring a Hotel Manager for our Kolkata team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Goa Tourism Holdings Services:\nGoa Tourism Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kolkata, West Bengal, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Goa Tourism Holdings Services!",
